rows.label: bf10010100_0020
rows.name:
Coriolis effect deviation detected
across the orbital ring.

rows.label: bf10010100_0030
rows.name:
Impact has caused a shift of point
two magnitude to the west-northwest.

rows.label: bf10010100_0060
rows.name:
Siren units attrition
rate has exceeded 60%.

rows.label: bf10010100_0070
rows.name:
Director, The entire Beanstal
won't hold at this rate!

rows.label: bf10010100_0080
rows.name:
It's only a matter of time before will
be occupied by the [System:Ruby rt=Salvator ]rebel forces[/System:Ruby].

rows.label: bf10010100_0140
rows.name:
Professor Klaus has
exclusive control over it.

rows.label: bf10010100_0150
rows.name: We cannot access it from here.

rows.label: bf10010100_0200
rows.name:
No! Stop! We haven't
confirmed the results yet!

rows.label: bf10010100_0230
rows.name:
We are about to witness the
birth of a universe...

rows.label: bf10010100_0240
rows.name:
...Indeed. This is a miracle
that only God could achieve.

rows.label: bf10010100_0250
rows.name:
The day humans take one step
closer to God has arrived.

rows.label: bf10010100_0270
rows.name:
Do you even understand
what that thing is?

rows.label: bf10010100_0280
rows.name:
So what's your alternative? Hand
this place over to them instead?

rows.label: bf10010100_0290
rows.name:
That thing is the hand
extended to us by God.

rows.label: bf10010100_0310
rows.name:
With it, we can journey to
an entirely new world.

rows.label: bf10010100_0325
rows.name: There is no such thing as God.

rows.label: bf10010100_0330
rows.name:
That thing is nothing
but a multiverse joint.

rows.label: bf10010100_0355
rows.name:
And now we're about to burn
even the skies themselves.

rows.label: bf10010100_0360
rows.name:
But that thing might change
us into supreme beings.

rows.label: bf10010100_0370
rows.name:
You could say it's the birth
of a new universe, Galatea.

rows.label: bf10010100_0500
rows.name:
Year 20XX [System:Ruby rt=Beanstalk ]Orbital Tower[/System:Ruby] First
Low Orbit Station: Rhadamanthus
